_sText:
I think I overdid the sprites a little...

Anyways, this is a small Christmas map I made for the holiday season here on FPSB. It's a DE map with bomb sites in the cabin's dining room and the outhouse. Yes, inside the outhouse.
As I said, it's a small map so I wouldn't recommend running it with a huge load of players, although the map supporst up to 32 players, if you 
really want to run it like that...

It is also my first ever CS:S map so yay for me for actually making a CS:S map... Although I don't play CS:S very much and therefore propably 
won't see the map "in action". I also don't expect too much from the map as it was only a small project for the holidays.
Hope you like it, and I don't care if you don't like it. :)

*** Merry Christmas, FPSBanana! ***
